{"tid":1673120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[選舉來了]對制度完全失去信任,區選爭議點解決?","createTime":"2019-10-24T13:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T03:54:15.000Z","uid":266548,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"aee2eba24ca7397f3735d1c1d3a0dffd138cc86f","tid":1673120,"uid":266548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">首先，呢個係共用ac唔好見我係P牌就當我三毛，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">請用論點論據理性討論</span></strong>。作為一個對制度完全失去信任嘅人，我係唔想大家又返入制度玩中共嘅偽民主選舉遊戲，原因如下：</span><br />\n<br />\n1.<strong>球證 旁證 加上主辦 協辦 所有單位 全部都係佢地嘅人</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Under現有systeｍ，根本無辦法確保選舉係公平公正。<br />\n選管會有權DQ候選人，票站會俾人做手腳，幽靈人口會出來種票：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">梁天琦票倉尚德突然多300票 票站主任不理反對重新點算</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20160905/55601197\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160905%2F55601197&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNgp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=ac5fccce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160905%2F55601197&h=82572672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20160905/55601197</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>【遺失選民登記冊】選舉事務處：涉葵青區 8000 人 資料包括身份證、有否投票等</strong></span></span><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KzpPrb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KzpPrb&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNgp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=cb579439\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KzpPrb</a>  (立場)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2019:【區選光復香港】再爆種票疑雲！同鄉會涉盜用資料 新選民2年前「被登記」</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191017/60163370\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191017%2F60163370&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNgp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=84fe29c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191017%2F60163370&h=44e93895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191017/60163370</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警渣選擇性執法，立法會有功能組別分組點票同廢左無分別，律政司玩程序玩法律，法官被染紅。根本行政立法執法司法都係佢地嘅人，點確保選舉結果係公平公正？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2.<strong>點兼顧制度外抗爭？</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果區選進行緊，會唔會又有人吹和風＂等區選完左先勇武，唔好俾口實林林鄭取消區選，勇武畫面好難睇會失民意（會無人投我地），遊行阻到自己友拉票etc...＂？</span></strong><br />\n勇武一停，大搜捕就會開始，點確保前線安危？<br />\n大家一入返去選舉mode，習慣用選戰代替抗爭，會唔會拖散運動？<br />\n會唔會有人會認為區選出左力其他戰線可以抖抖，變相令運動轉化為選戰？<br />\n如果選戰蓋過制度外抗爭，國際戰線會唔會覺得香港人可以用制度解決問題，減少關注同幫助？<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong>目的同成效</strong><br />\n有人話區選大勝代表民意，但我認為制度外行動更代表到香港人民真正想追求民主自由嘅意志同更有效追求到民主自由。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>如果係想攞資源支持抗爭/唔俾保皇黨攞資源，一來我地肯定唔到區選會否大勝(因為種票做手腳etc.)，二來單純唔俾保皇黨攞資源，咁搞唔成區選唔係更公平同簡單(兩邊都無資源)？(我認為解決到種票等問題，區選係值得參與，因為可以由地區開始光復。)<br />\n如果係想透過區選攞立法會議席去影響一個小圈子特首選舉，會唔會太唔effective同efficient ?<br />\n都係嗰句我地肯定唔到區選會否大勝，大勝後會否被人DQ。<br />\n就算呢兩樣無發生，特首選舉一定有我地支持嘅人入到閘？入到閘我地咩都做唔到等小圈子幫我地揀？贏左中央唔任命大家會點？<br />\n做咁多野都只係為左一個壞左嘅制度入面贏？</strong></span></span><br />\n理念係用行動實踐，唔係選左代議士就解決到香港問題。<br />\n如果選票解決到，咁點解我地６月９日仲要行出來？<br />\n請大家傾下。"},{"pid":"46ef1dd0846e6534099030b478148c6f9c4633a1","tid":1673120,"uid":266548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:06:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"228291e94e988df256cdd85d7bf60d7ca93f4617","tid":1673120,"uid":34336,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:06:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b8232ddbcc5b66ddde5f2b6cb212df1686a36ae","tid":1673120,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:07:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d7644b0f6dda4b9c7872e4779d20ed0f268371d","tid":1673120,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:08:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f0288271f7450ca79ac83b216ec44ed032f6e07","tid":1673120,"uid":53306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:08:45.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"1eed4951a0d8ceb7906b3ae7165a00897f5f8b3f","tid":1673120,"uid":53306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:08:55.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"c9b7ccaa2f4ed2e05e3f8ce46ea5a797547a54b8","tid":1673120,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:08:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b528d537f20e169f709f08b6f5c429842b847671","tid":1673120,"uid":4062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:09:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ace365d83cc305851bbb7ccf14f7a6992130f865","tid":1673120,"uid":51133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:09:16.000Z","msg":"嚟"},{"pid":"d4db6b6190cb48250699b0b892df227f94104d2d","tid":1673120,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:09:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c11afda78b1879e8d8f8702fe3eedd62e34e7ee","tid":1673120,"uid":47110,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:09:46.000Z","msg":"唔可以放棄區選<br />\n因為如果我地放棄左而令親共派大勝 支共就大條道理話佢地有沉默大多數支持<br />\n<br />\n所以區選一定要玩 仲一定要大勝 同時要加強文宣keep住街頭抗爭"},{"pid":"55b2ef106f4255b203fca974149e0e1b4dc59abf","tid":1673120,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/itbR4in.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FitbR4in.jpg&h=bd7ae3e5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"81288217cf0a4838e5ed7e05bfdf0c0fa8d00004","tid":1673120,"uid":296079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB